body:
So, I've been on this server for more than enough time (2 years +) and finally decided to make a intro! I recently got CS:GO and absolutely love it. But that was taking a ton of time out of spending time and having a great time on TS. After a hard decision I decided to get back into Avicus :D( I still play csgo once a day at least) you'll see me on Avicus and on ts most of the day.I'm currently on the team liquidators :D And 1v1ing new and old people everyday! I also will start to reupload to my new channel!
(Finally got a 720-1080p recorder!) Also, if you have any questions, Ask!

Birdy












































































































And, I don't know why I'm saying this but I'm a going to a water park tomorrow :D
